title: Ep. 6 - The great divide
itunes:title: Ep. 6 - The great divide
description:
Gen Z has spoken, and the side part is out. They say it makes you look old.
 
Excuse us? This one feels a wee bit personal, and Wendy goes to the mat on behalf of The Olds.
